# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Private company data — NEVER committed to this public repo
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# User-specific REN folders (business content, internal procedure names, etc.)
ren/REN_*

# User-specific procedure knowledge (real SP names and business logic)
docs/procedures/*
!docs/procedures/_TEMPLATE.md
!docs/procedures/.gitkeep

# User-specific learning log and accumulated decisions
docs/learning-log.md
docs/technical-decisions.md
docs/side-effects-catalog.md

# Re-include the public starter templates
!docs/learning-log.md.template
!docs/technical-decisions.md.template
!docs/side-effects-catalog.md.template
